snippet.title: Later Daters Release Date Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
In this visual novel dating sim, play as an octogenarian and find somebody to love, or just get your kicks in while the getting is good. Remember, if the chairs are rockin', don't come knockin'.

Coming to Switch, Itch.io and Steam April 16, 2020.

Wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1040390/Later_Daters/


Later Daters theme by: Veda Hille.
